phrases: Vapor pressure stabilized.
It should work this time.
Right!
Open the valve!
At last.
At last, we have done it!
Now the Kingdom can finally crush the Commonwealth!
Long live the Kingdom of Albion!
Now we just have to work on mass production.
You will see what you get for stealing our country!
What is our target?
A C-ball.
The Kingdom has successfully miniaturized the Cavorite control unit.
I would like your team to take the prototype from them.
So the main players in this shadow war are the spies and the scientists.
The Kingdom possesses refining technology that we lack.
If they combine it with the miniature control unit,
they would make large-scale gravity weapons a reality.
If not handled carefully, this could change history.
Is not this a bit much for a team with amateurs?
Our more experienced spies could...
This is something only your team can do.
Because of Princess?
She is your team's strong point.
You will use her position to infiltrate the ceremony at the Cavorite mine.
Honestly, the way you work that princess...
Another thing, Dorothy...
This is for your ears only.
Beatrice, switch.
Checkmate.
Your turn, Beatrice.
You will not shake me this time.
You keep saying that, and yet you have lost ten times in a row.
You have been losing right along with me, Miss Chise.
I have been victorious once.
It does not count as winning when you cut down a police officer.
Fear not.
I used the back of my sword.
And that makes it better?
Indeed it does.
Say, I have been thinking.
You do not suppose our team could use a name, do you?
That is a wonderful idea!
They do say names and natures often agree.
We do not need a team name.
We do not want to make up any information that could turn up as evidence.
That is an ironclad spy rule.
Is that why you tell nothing but lies?
If I am a liar, then there is no point in questioning me, is there?
We are all girls, so I think we should have a cute name.
Something pink, or a flower.
What about the name of that unusual bird we saw the other day?
I think it was a penguin?
Just a moment.
I will do an onomancy reading for that name.
This is the Security Service!
Open the door!
You could be a little scared, Partner.
Did you get to see L?
Yes, and he gave us the most annoying target.
And you?
We were thinking of team names.
We were practicing tailing.
Ooh, team names, is it?
All right, I will be Scotch, Ange will be Calvados,
Princess will be Champagne...
Chise, let us see...
They are all the names of liquors, are not they?
Chise, let us see...
They are all the names of liquors, are not they?
Do not be a part of this, Dorothy.
They need to learn basic tailing techni-
Oh no!
How do I count the strokes of the letters in your alphabet?
It is like a mechanical fortress.
Cavorite is the heart and soul of Albion's Air Fleet.
Naturally, the mines will be heavily guarded.
Excuse me.
Are you here for the ceremony?
Hello, there.
Princess!
I brought some friends from school with me.
Is that all right?
I beg your pardon.
The power of a nation's princess.
If they tried to body check her, heads would roll.
So I am a key, then?
Yes, a magic one.
The ceremony starts in 30 minutes.
With guests arriving and preparations underway, this will be their busiest time.
In other words, the time when security is the most lax.
And we will use that time to get the prototype from the underground laboratory!
You all know the plan, right?
Dorothy, Beatrice, and I will infiltrate the facility.
Her Majesty the Queen is here.
If you would be so kind...
Of course.
Princess, we will be a-waitin' right over there.
I am leaving Chise here to protect you.
She is our most reliable fighter.
One guard.
What do we do?
Looks like I am up.
Um, just wh-what are you...?
Huh?
Another dead end?
You can take the stairs to the right.
Then go straight ahead to the ceremony hall.
Thanks f'r the directions!
I think I drank too much.
Could you get me something to drink?
I-if water will suffice.
Oh, you are so kind!
Wh..what are you-?
You have such a cute face, Mr. Guard Man.
Do... do you really... think so?
What the...?
Hey!
Is that you, Jake?
There is been a methane explosion!
So that is where the dust is coming from!
I will take over here!
You go get some masks!
They are in Storeroom Three.
Three?
That is all the way on the other side!
Give me a break!
I am already beat from helping with the move!
Miss Ange, all clear.
We would better hurry.
We have about 20 minutes until they get back.
Miss Ange, I have been thinking.
What?
What do you think about Team Wildcat?
They are so swift and fearless.
But they look adorable!
Would you... change your voice back?
It is unsettling.
How do you do, Grandmother?
We have not seen you since the ceremony at the music academy.
How is school?
I have made some good friends.
That is good to hear.
Friends can be life-long treasures.
Yes, Grandmother.
What do you think of the princess?
She is not what I imagined.
She is royalty, but she speaks to us as equals.
She even tells jokes.
But none of them are very funny.
She is full of curiosity, and always giving Ange trouble.
Chise.
I trust they do not suspect you?
They removed me from the infiltration team.
We are here to find out whether we can trust the Kingdom or the Commonwealth.
We must choose which to ally ourselves with.
Yes, Sir.
I understand.
Your Majesty, I believe it is time.
For what?
To discuss marriage.
Mine?
We told you, it is too soon.
Such matters can wait until after she has graduated.
I beg your pardon, Majesty,
but strengthening our relationship with Moscow will lead to the stabilization of all of Europe.
And to that end you would have Us sacrifice Our own granddaughter?
Binding our countries through marriage will squelch the possibility of a world war.
From here on, I go alone.
If I am not back in ten minutes, you go back to the others.
All right.
Please be careful.
Oh?
Did you leave Ange and Beatrice?
Yeah, well, you know...
Will they be all right?
You are worried?
Yes, of course.
This is for your ears only.
This mission will deal a damaging blow to the Kingdom.
If Princess is a double agent, she is sure to take action.
You mean...?
We have not abandoned the possibility that Princess is our enemy.
Is something the matter?
Oh, no.
I was just wondering what would make a good team name.
Miss Ange has been gone a long time.
No...
Was there a leak?
No, even if there was...
This is some big equipment.
This definitely would have been the research facility.
Give me a break!
I am already beat from helping with the move!
They moved it?
Up there?
This is...
Miss Dorothy!
Beatrice?
Where is Ange?
She told me to leave without her if she did not come back in ten minutes.
Really.
She must be having some trouble, then.
I hope she is all right.
Come with me.
Let us go, Princess.
What is the matter?
There is no time.
I will explain on the way.
What is going on?
Apparently they moved the entire laboratory.
Was there an information leak?
I do not know.
But I found the loading dock they used.
It leads to the Thames.
So they escaped by boat?
The drawbridge only opened up ten minutes ago.
They cannot have gotten far.
If we take the shortest route, we should catch up to them at Greenwich.
Got it!
Our research was finally on the right track.
Why should we have to move NOW?
In answer to your question, I would like you to look at this.
What does that book have to do with anything?
You will see.
A camera?
There is a Commonwealth spy in our midst.
We will now conduct a VERY thorough investigation.
Left at the next corner.
Right at the next intersection.
Right at the next stairway.
You got it!
Stairway?
But we are in an automobile!
Do not bite your tongue.
How do you feel about Team Meikyo Shisui?
(Mirror-smooth Water)
How do you feel about Team Meikyo Shisui?
What does it mean?
Next, through that narrow passage up ahead and turn left!
Nobody fall out!
Be quiet.
There it is.
We made it!
I thought maybe Princess had leaked the information, but...
It is quite the large boat, is not it?
At that size, it could be carrying an entire platoon.
I will go with you.
No.
You stay here, Chise.
Dorothy and I will go alone.
You would leave me behind again?
Miss Chise...?
I am a stronger asset than Dorothy!
I know.
Then why...
You came to us under the graces of Lord Horikawa.
We cannot ask you to put yourself in danger.
Your concern is unnecessary!
I said I would go!
Your Highness?
I am going, too.
No, you cannot!
I have been trained.
Besides, if I go, you will not have to leave a guard with me.
Wait a minute, Princess.
This is not some party we are talking about.
It is too dangerous for an amateur.
I would like to know why you are so eager to take the risk.
Come now, I have been in danger all along.
If word gets out that I am a spy, it is over for me.
I am standing on a precipice... a bridge much narrower and more fragile than this one.
That is no reason to put yourself in MORE danger!
It is the same either way.
If you all fail, that will lead them directly to my secret.
And in that case,
I must put my life on the line to make this plan succeed.
If Princess is a double agent,
it should not matter if her secret gets out- she would have a safety net.
There would be no reason to take such a big risk.
All right, Princess.
We are on this boat together, then.
Yes!
What was that?
Did you kill him?
He was not strong enough to merit killing.
What do we do now?
We split into two groups.
Princess and I will go aft.
Right.
We will take the bow, then.
Charlotte.
Are you angry?
Of course I am, after that stunt...
I was worried sick.
I am sorry.
Meanie.
You like to see me squirm.
Can you blame me, Charlotte?
You act like I am the only important one.
Because...
When we were children, you talked to me like normal.
If I did that now, people would know we are old friends.
But we are ALL friends.
All right, then, why do not we say we met and realized we are kindred spirits?
Then we would not have to hide our friendship.
No.
I would lose control of myself.
I think it is good to let your hair down on occasion.
Like you used to.
I hate who I used to be.
But it is the old you
that I love so much.
You have finally shown your true colors.
What?!
The Cavorite research team, I presume?
We would like you to come with us.
You are...
You cannot be...
We are spies.
We have not settled on a name yet.
Not only did we get the prototype, but we have the researchers in custody.
The results were even better than we hoped.
Now Princess is clear of all suspicion.
No.
This world is not black and white.
Only black and grey.
And the princess is grey.
Keep a constant watch on her.
All right, then.
As part of the food series, let us be Team Carrot!
These are getting worse and worse.
I do not especially like carrots.
Your Highness!
You must not be picky!
I know.
What about Team White Pigeon?
Pigeon?
Not bad.
It is pretty and cute.
I like it!
They do call spies pigeons.
Really?
After the Flood, Noah sent a dove... a pigeon... to scout for land.
Then that settles it.
What do you think, Miss Dorothy?
I like it.
Team White Pigeon.
I especially like that it is not grey.
I knew you would like it!
